      }
    },
    "Press Esc to discard without transcribing. Active only while recording so it doesn't steal Esc from other apps when you're not dictating." : {
      "comment" : "Help Basics — Cancel-recording sub-row prose",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Press Esc to discard without transcribing. Active only while recording so it doesn't steal Esc from other apps when you're not dictating." } },
        "ja" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "new", "value" : "" } }
      }
    },
    "Esc is hardcoded, not configurable. macOS global hotkeys must include a modifier — Esc is an exception reserved for canceling in-flight transformations." : {
